About us
Beaker & Flask, located in Alachua's San Felasco Tech City, is a destination for exceptional wine experiences. We offer global varietals, a wine club, tastings, and private events with expert guidance. Honored with Wine Spectator's Award of Excellence in 2023 and 2024, we celebrate the finest wines.
Beaker & Flask is Alachua's wine destination. We serve a robust selection of wine varietals from around the world, expert knowledge to support your wine selection, exceptional service, wine club, private events, wine tastings, wine education, and wine cellar curation. We were honored with the Wine Spectator's Award of Excellence two years in a row, published in its August 2023 and 2024 issues.
Our service executes on the hospitality quotient of kindness and optimism, intellectual curiosity, work ethic, empathy, self-awareness, and integrity.We are located in Alachua's San Felasco Tech City, next to Daft Cow Brewery.
